            . I live at Hackney. On the 22d of June, between four and five o'clock, I was in <placeName id="t18220703-99-crimeloc517">Nortonfalgate</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18220703-99-crimeloc517" type="placeName" value="Nortonfalgate"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18220703-99-crimeloc517" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220703-99-off515 t18220703-99-crimeloc517"></join>, and felt a slight touch at my pocket - I missed my handkerchief, turned round, and saw the prisoner and another boy standing close together; I laid hold of them, and saw my handkerchief drop from the prisoner's hand; I kept him, but the other got off. He said a boy gave it him.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18220703-99-person861">
                  THOMAS 
                  VANN
